                    <p class="lead">Ebates is an affiliate company. Retailers will pay affiliates money to send traffic to their websites. Ebates takes that commission and splits it with you.</p><p class="lead"> See <%= link_to 'example', "#", :id => 'example-btn' %>.<br>           
